 6.5



Solid waste disposal sites in operation on September 1, 1984. 



(a) The operator of a solid waste disposal site in operation 
as of September 1, 1984, within the boundaries of a unit of the 
National Park System, having been in continuous operation on 
January 23, 1995, and who wishes to remain in 
operation, must submit to the proper Superintendent for review by 
the Regional Director, within 180 calendar days of January 23, 1995, a permit request and an environmental 
