of which shall not exceed five years. The permittee may request a new five year permit upon expiration of an existing
permit. The permit instrument will be Form 10-114 (OMB No. 1024-0026), Special Use Permit, available
from the park Superintendent. 
(e) A permit for a solid waste disposal site will prescribe the site capacity and the requirements under which the solid
