(10) Methods of excluding waste generated from non-National Park Service activities, except for a solid waste disposal
site approved under  6.5, or  6.6, or  6.7(c); and 
(11) Methods of litter control. 
(f) Any conflict between a requirement of the permit issued by the National Park Service and a requirement of State
or local law will be resolved in favor of the stricter of the two requirements. 


 6.10 


Financial assurance. 


(a) The Regional Director will not require a bond or security deposit for a solid waste disposal site for which the operator
